channel.title: Foxscape v9 - w/Webclient
channel.description:
The server and client is Deception based. To play correctly you will need to Deception client or use the webclient. Cache must be downloaded first and be stored in
[code]C:/Users/UserName[/code]
Features are still the same until I can add more stuff such as a training ground and other stuff.
- Great Economy - Shops on Quest Interface - Special Attacks - Torva Armor - Some items you probably though you'd never see again. - All Deception Based - Fixed NPC Spawns. Now 99% RS Spawns. - Webclient ready to use. Just download cache
[center][url=http://profox.netau.net/webclient.html][img]http://profox.netau.net/images/play.png[/img][/url] [url=http://profox.netau.net/download.html][img]http://profox.netau.net/images/download.png[/img][/url][/center]
[center] [img]http://profox.netau.net/images/login.png[/img] [img]http://profox.netau.net/images/torva.png[/img] [img]http://profox.netau.net/images/wood.png[/img] [img]http://profox.netau.net/images/specs.png[/img] [img]http://profox.netau.net/images/loot.png[/img] [/center]
